data.title: Marine Environmental Data and Information Network
data.text:
The MEDIN Portalâ€‹

The MEDIN portal describes over 18,000 marine datasets, owned or managed by more than 600 UK organisations.

The MEDIN data discovery portal is a service to allow users, through a single point of access, to find information on marine datasets held at the Data Archive Centres or at other public and private sector bodies.

Use the MEDIN Portal
